body:
@yuanbyu thanks for prompt reply. Well, yes, in such simple case this works.

However, imagine that `c1` is `GruCell`. It is forbidden to access such computational nodes that are not passed directly by scan from the inner function (afaik).

@vojtsek could give more description of the problem with scan and using the variable that are not passed by it.
